Class RoleCommandOrder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.metadata.RoleCommandOrder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable

    public class RoleCommandOrder
extends Object
implements Cloneable
    This class is used to establish the order between two roles. This class should not be used to determine the dependencies.

      • getSectionKeys

        public LinkedHashSet<String> getSectionKeys()
        Gets the collection of section names that was used to initialize this RoleCommandOrder instance. If this instance has not been initialized, this will be null.

        The ordering of this collection is maintained.

        Returns:
        the section keys used to initialize this instance or null if it has not been initialized.
